trans-unit.source: Represents the AppSequence header defined in the WS-Discovery protocol.
trans-unit.target: Representa definido no protocolo WS-Discovery no cabeçalho AppSequence.

trans-unit.source: This class allows a receiver of discovery messages to process those messages in order even though they were received out of order.
trans-unit.target: Esta classe permite um recetor de mensagens de deteção para processar as mensagens por ordem, apesar de foram recebidas fora de ordem.
